<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>찾기 결과</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 40px; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; }
        .box { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 20px; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="box">
    <% if (type === 'id' && foundUsername) { %>
        <h2>아이디 찾기 결과</h2>
        <p>회원님의 아이디는 다음과 같습니다.</p>
        <h3 style="background: #f0f4f8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; color: #2563eb;"><%= foundUsername %></h3>
        <a href="/user/login" class="btn">로그인하러 가기</a>

    <% } else if (type === 'pw' && verifiedUser) { %>
        <h2>🔒 새 비밀번호 설정</h2>
        <p>본인 확인이 완료되었습니다.<br>새로운 비밀번호를 입력해 주세요.</p>

        <form action="/user/reset-pw" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="username" value="<%= verifiedUser %>">
            <input type="password" name="newPassword" placeholder="새 비밀번호 입력" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn" style="background-color: #e53e3e; border: none; width: 100%; cursor: pointer;">비밀번호 변경하기</button>
        </form>
    <% } %>
</div>

</body>
</html>